00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:52.400
Come on, we'll be late.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:19.850
Why don't you go out with anyone, Ren?

00:13:19.850 --> 00:13:21.980
Because I already have a girlfriend.

00:13:21.980 --> 00:13:23.880
What? Since when?

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:26.510
Since... just the other day, I think.

00:13:26.510 --> 00:13:28.390
Who?

00:13:28.390 --> 00:13:30.040
She's not from our school.

00:13:30.040 --> 00:13:32.130
Then what middle school does she go to?

00:13:32.130 --> 00:13:34.890
- She's a high schooler.
- Say what?

00:13:45.870 --> 00:13:47.390
Ando.

00:13:47.390 --> 00:13:48.770
Yeah?

00:13:49.400 --> 00:13:55.240
You're always hanging out with Ichinose, right?

00:14:00.100 --> 00:14:06.950
Do you know if he has a girlfriend?

00:14:11.260 --> 00:14:12.990
He does.

00:14:16.540 --> 00:14:18.440
I see.

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:25.850
Sorry to bother you.

00:14:34.860 --> 00:14:36.750
I like you.

00:14:42.140 --> 00:14:46.320
Here. A present to commemorate our one month anniversary.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.090
Thanks!

00:14:49.050 --> 00:14:52.950
Mao. Do you like me?

00:14:52.950 --> 00:14:54.940
You're asking me again?

00:14:56.920 --> 00:14:58.670
Of course I like you.

00:16:14.510 --> 00:16:16.500
- Mao.
- Yeah?

00:16:16.500 --> 00:16:18.510
Do you like me?

00:16:19.840 --> 00:16:21.530
Of course I like you.

00:16:32.380 --> 00:16:34.880
Well, I hate you.

00:16:46.040 --> 00:16:47.460
He did it again.

00:16:47.460 --> 00:16:49.200
- Seriously?
- Yikes.

00:16:49.200 --> 00:16:51.350
I guess that's Ichinose for you.

00:16:51.350 --> 00:16:54.240
- What a disaster.
- It's straight terrifying, man.

00:17:00.690 --> 00:17:05.020
It's not your fault I broke up with Mao, okay?

00:17:13.250 --> 00:17:15.460
Ando...

00:17:15.460 --> 00:17:18.970
We're still best buds, you hear me?

00:17:18.970 --> 00:17:22.110
We won't let a little girl trouble ruin our friendship.

00:17:49.110 --> 00:17:52.000
Can't believe I'm waking up to a guy.

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:53.980
