00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:06.800
What, you feel bad for me?

00:18:06.800 --> 00:18:09.660
I don't need your pity.

00:18:10.600 --> 00:18:16.110
We're not even best friends or anything.

00:18:16.110 --> 00:18:17.640
Not anymore.

00:18:22.890 --> 00:18:28.850
Why do you always shut up and let things pass? It pisses me off.

00:18:29.820 --> 00:18:32.020
We've been through this already.

00:18:32.020 --> 00:18:34.200
When Mao kissed you.

00:18:36.960 --> 00:18:39.450
Why didn't you ever say anything about it?

00:18:40.870 --> 00:18:44.220
You could have at least tried to make an excuse.

00:18:44.980 --> 00:18:47.040
What was I supposed to say?

00:18:49.850 --> 00:18:54.300
What did you want me to say?

00:19:00.390 --> 00:19:02.700
In any case, you still would've...

00:19:08.390 --> 00:19:09.960
Whatever.

00:19:09.960 --> 00:19:11.750
Stupid Ando.

00:19:11.750 --> 00:19:14.450
Takes one to know one, Stupid!

00:19:19.010 --> 00:19:21.300
Did Ando wake up?

00:19:21.300 --> 00:19:23.030
Yes.

00:19:23.030 --> 00:19:24.600
You doing alright?

00:19:25.690 --> 00:19:27.010
Yes.

00:19:29.240 --> 00:19:32.190
"You should speak up when you're not feeling well."

00:19:33.020 --> 00:19:35.290
Remember?

00:19:40.690 --> 00:19:42.230
How're you feeling?

00:19:45.820 --> 00:19:48.200
I hate feeling like this.

00:19:49.580 --> 00:19:51.640
Just let me disappear.

00:20:11.730 --> 00:20:13.150
Ren.

00:20:13.150 --> 00:20:14.800
Kinoshita.

00:20:14.800 --> 00:20:17.260
How was Ando?

00:20:17.260 --> 00:20:19.150
He was just feeling a bit dizzy.

00:20:19.150 --> 00:20:22.030
He should be fine after a bit of rest.

00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:23.770
That's good to hear.

00:20:31.100 --> 00:20:33.210
Say...

00:20:35.730 --> 00:20:37.250
Yeah?

00:20:39.100 --> 00:20:44.620
Can't friends be friends, even if the feeling's not mutual?

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:51.580
Sorry, weird question.

00:20:54.910 --> 00:20:59.210
Did you get into an argument with a friend?

00:21:01.600 --> 00:21:05.540
I always knew our relationship had gotten rocky.

00:21:05.540 --> 00:21:11.450
So I just assumed I wasn't allowed to call him a friend anymore.

00:21:16.130 --> 00:21:19.100
Sorry, it's a bit complicated.

00:21:20.970 --> 00:21:25.040
But I feel better now after talking it out.

00:21:26.510 --> 00:21:28.390
Thanks for lending me an ear.

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:30.390
Sure.

00:21:34.820 --> 00:21:39.530
Ren only tells well-meaning white lies.

00:21:52.380 --> 00:21:55.590
I couldn't give him any advice.

00:22:02.150 --> 00:22:05.480
I promise I feel better, really.

00:22:06.760 --> 00:22:08.240
See you around.

00:22:19.970 --> 00:22:21.670
Excuse me.

00:22:23.860 --> 00:22:27.620
I believe you were with Takumi yesterday?

00:22:27.620 --> 00:22:29.330
I was, yes.

00:22:29.330 --> 00:22:33.010
Are you Takumi's girlfriend?

00:22:33.550 --> 00:22:35.580
No.

00:22:37.560 --> 00:22:39.210
Then...

00:22:40.890 --> 00:22:43.990
Do you have a crush on Ichinose?

00:22:44.970 --> 00:22:46.360
What?

00:23:05.900 --> 00:23:09.390
Ren and I are only friends.

00:23:09.390 --> 00:23:11.980
We'll be splitting up into groups for the school trip.

00:23:11.980 --> 00:23:14.250
I regret breaking up with you, Uehara.

00:23:14.250 --> 00:23:18.270
Sincerity is guaranteed to be a straight shot to the heart.

00:23:18.270 --> 00:23:21.090
I'm confessing to Kinoshita after Sports Day.

00:23:21.090 --> 00:23:23.640
- What?
- Just admiring you, Futaba.

00:23:23.640 --> 00:23:27.990
I know I won't be able to hold these feelings back forever.

00:23:27.990 --> 00:23:30.200
Even though I'm right at his side,

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:35.320
I'm the closest, yet furthest I've been from him.

00:23:35.320 --> 00:23:39.090
[Epilogue]

00:23:45.230 --> 00:23:47.860
Excuse me, have you seen Takumi?

00:23:47.860 --> 00:23:50.200
